Mini Search Engine (TF-IDF + Semantic Search + Autocomplete)

A fully functional search engine built from scratch â€” including a web crawler, inverted index, TF-IDF ranking, semantic search using MiniLM embeddings, and autocomplete using Trie, with a React UI front-end.

